174c7228f7f0b6cfb5b677723","tid":2293061,"uid":70014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:57:21.000Z","msg":"唔該晒各位師兄"},{"pid":"bc3c686fbace3fcf4bb1b3b2c558cbb027322dc6","tid":2293061,"uid":116960,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:10:59.000Z","msg":"上面班友講BRANCH,MASTER堆野我諗對於一個連GITHUB係咩的人黎講應該都係唔明。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW GIT可能理解成VERSION CONTROL軟件。例如你有一個.txt文件但同時兩條友改。個.txt文件有一百萬行字。<br />\n同事A改左第一行,同時間同事B改左第一百萬行,咁姐係而家同事A個VERSION同同事B個VERSION唔同,GIT就係幫兩位同事RECORD低對家改左咩同你而家個FILE有咩唔同,然後你再選擇樓上所講MERGE/開新BRANCH動作。而GITHUB你就當係GIT的WEB版啦"},{"pid":"3cc68aa44c01ce32b9e5330ca8236d9be109f125","tid":2293061,"uid":11849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"Svn簡單易用易明啲<br />\nGit到宜家我都唔太明分local remote作用<br />\n求解答"},{"pid":"d5e4a277d6e2f798f9b74002f10179943c1fee70","tid":2293061,"uid":70014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc3c686fbace3fcf4bb1b3b2c558cbb027322dc6","tid":2293061,"uid":116960,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:10:59.000Z","msg":"上面班友講BRANCH,MASTER堆野我諗對於一個連GITHUB係咩的人黎講應該都係唔明。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW GIT可能理解成VERSION CONTROL軟件。例如你有一個.txt文件但同時兩條友改。個.txt文件有一百萬行字。<br />\n同事A改左第一行,同時間同事B改左第一百萬行,咁姐係而家同事A個VERSION同同事B個VERSION唔同,GIT就係幫兩位同事RECORD低對家改左咩同你而家個FILE有咩唔同,然後你再選擇樓上所講MERGE/開新BRANCH動作。而GITHUB你就當係GIT的WEB版啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"好詳細 多謝師兄"},{"pid":"399d62f33d6d37b8d7d6d1ce837dea551c02b91e","tid":2293061,"uid":73565,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3cc68aa44c01ce32b9e5330ca8236d9be109f125","tid":2293061,"uid":11849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"Svn簡單易用易明啲<br />\nGit到宜家我都唔太明分local remote作用<br />\n求解答"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"Git係成個repo扯落黎<br />\n話之你local攪到龍飛鳳舞<br />\n一日唔push都唔會影響到server<br />\nSvn一commit就上去"},{"pid":"6762f60777624b7cf9d869ab202f7716fef991a8","tid":2293061,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T00:58:31.000Z","msg":"無撚用的識來做咩<br />\n<br />\n學下炒股好過"},{"pid":"f2243edca7ed037090368428fa08a6686451cdb7","tid":2293061,"uid":273613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"等人set好git repository (remote)<br />\n跟住你用git 條link 拉左落黎(即係pull)  save/merge落自己部機度 (local branch), <br />\n咁你每做小小function就 搵git explorer ,揀晒你要update既file (唔好揀bin folder)   add落stage list (待commit) , 然後commit staged左既file再push , 就會push 去orign/你既branch<br />\n然後再同master , orign/master合併.."},{"pid":"01d923dde8ae9a09bf8afd2a67d3e8a89b2d5044","tid":2293061,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"人地assignment放上去分享"},{"pid":"4761ea3b5cd1a4ebe96d7938f07c4b8bb82b0e21","tid":2293061,"uid":79869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:14:12.000Z","msg":"Github明明係個全球最大同性交友網站，點解無人提<br />\n<img src=\"https://upclinux.github.io/intro/images/development/gayhub.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupclinux.github.io%2Fintro%2Fimages%2Fdevelopment%2Fgayhub.png&h=a968487e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5aa09170ef4150a79c2b09f22909cc871370e6da","tid":2293061,"uid":79869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3cc68aa44c01ce32b9e5330ca8236d9be109f125","tid":2293061,"uid":11849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"Svn簡單易用易明啲<br />\nGit到宜家我都唔太明分local remote作用<br />\n求解答"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"svn係centralized, 需要1台center server, 所有user都要連進去才能用svn, <span class=\"red\">不能offline使用, 不存在local commit</span><br />\ngit係distributed, 不需要center server, 所有user自己就能獨立地使用git, 能<span class=\"red\">夠offline使用, 可以local commit</span>"}]}